Node_String_Regex_Match.name: RegEx Match
Node_String_Regex_Match.tooltip: Check whether regular expression pattern exist in a string.

Node_String_Regex_Replace.name: RegEx Replace
Node_String_Regex_Replace.tooltip: Replace instances of a string with another using regular expression.

Node_String_Regex_Search.name: RegEx Search
Node_String_Regex_Search.tooltip: Search for instances in a string using regular expression.

Node_String_Split.name: Split Text
Node_String_Split.tooltip: Split string into arrays of substring based on delimiter.

inputs.name: Delimiter
inputs.tooltip:
Character that used to split text,
leave blank to create character array.

Node_String_Trim.name: Trim Text
Node_String_Trim.tooltip: Remove first and last n character(s) from a string.

inputs.name: Mode
inputs.tooltip: Set to progress to use ratio, where 0 means no change and 1 means the entire length of the text.

Node_Struct_Get.name: Struct Get
Node_Struct_Get.tooltip: Get value from struct and key.

Node_Surface_From_Buffer.name: Surface from Buffer
Node_Surface_From_Buffer.tooltip: Create surface from a valid buffer.

Node_Surface_Replace.name: Replace Image
Node_Surface_Replace.tooltip: Replace instances of an image with a new one.

inputs.name: Color Threshold
inputs.tooltip: How similiar the color need to be in order to be count as matched.

inputs.name: Pixel Threshold
inputs.tooltip: How many pixel need to me matched to replace with replacement image.

Node_Texture_Remap.name: Texture Remap
Node_Texture_Remap.tooltip: Remap image using texture map. Where red channel control x position and green channel control y position.

Node_Threshold.name: Threshold
Node_Threshold.tooltip: Set a threshold where pixel darker will becomes black, and brighter to white. Also works with alpha.

Node_Tile.name: Tile
Node_Tile.tooltip: Repeat images on a larger surface.

Node_Tile_Convert.name: Convert to Tilemap
Node_Tile_Convert.tooltip: Convert color image to tile data.

Node_Tile_Random.name: Tile Random
Node_Tile_Random.tooltip: Repeat images on a larger surface randomly.

Node_Time_Remap.name: Time Remap
Node_Time_Remap.tooltip: Remap image using texture as time map. Where brighter pixel in time map means using pixel from an older frame.

Node_To_Number.name: To Number
Node_To_Number.tooltip: Convert string to number, supports scientific format (e.g. 1e-2 = 0.02).

Node_Trail.name: Trail
Node_Trail.tooltip: Blend animation by filling in the pixel 'in-between' two or more frames.

inputs.name: Max Distance
inputs.tooltip: Maximum distance to search for movement, set to -1 to search the entire image.

inputs.name: Match Color
inputs.tooltip: Make trail track pixels of the same color, instead of the closet pixels.

inputs.name: Blend Color
inputs.tooltip: Blend color between two pixel smoothly.

inputs.name: Rotate by Velocity
inputs.tooltip: Make the surface rotates to follow its movement.

inputs.name: Round Position
inputs.tooltip: Round position to the nearest integer value to avoid jittering.

Node_Trigger_Bool.name: Boolean Trigger
Node_Trigger_Bool.tooltip: Create trigger based on boolean condition.

Node_Tunnel_In.name: Tunnel Sender
Node_Tunnel_In.tooltip: Create tunnel for sending value based on key matching.

Node_Tunnel_Out.name: Tunnel Receiver
Node_Tunnel_Out.tooltip: Receive value from tunnel in of the same key.

Node_Twirl.name: Twirl
Node_Twirl.tooltip: Twist the image around a mid point.

inputs.name: Oversample Mode
inputs.tooltip:
How to deal with pixel outside the surface.
    - Empty: Use empty pixel
    - Clamp: Repeat edge pixel
    - Repeat: Repeat texture.

inputs.name: Show on global
inputs.tooltip: Whether to show overlay gizmo when not selecting any nodes.

Node_Vector_Cart_To_Polar.name: Cart. to Polar
Node_Vector_Cart_To_Polar.tooltip: Convert cartesian coordinates to polar coordinates

Node_Vector_Polar_To_Cart.name: Polar to Cart.
Node_Vector_Polar_To_Cart.tooltip: Convert polar coordinates to cartesian coordinates.

Node_Vector_Swizzle.tooltip: Rearrange vector using string containing axis indicies (x, y, z, w).

Node_VFX_Attract.tooltip: Attract particle in range to one point.

Node_VFX_Boids.name: Boids
Node_VFX_Boids.tooltip: Apply boids algorithm to create a flock behaviour.

Node_VFX_Group_Inline.name: VFX
Node_VFX_Group_Inline.tooltip: Create VFX group, which generate particles that can be manipulated using different force nodes.

Node_VFX_Oscillate.name: Oscillate
Node_VFX_Oscillate.tooltip: Swing particle around its original trajectory.

Node_VFX_Override.tooltip: Replace particle variable with a new one.

inputs.name: Round position
inputs.tooltip: Round position to the closest integer value to avoid jittering.

inputs.name: Spawn Delay
inputs.tooltip: Frames delay between each particle spawn.

inputs.tooltip: Amount of particle spawn in that frame.

inputs.name: Rotate by Direction
inputs.tooltip: Make the particle rotates to follow its movement.

inputs.name: Surface Array
inputs.tooltip: Whether to select image from an array in order, at random, or treat array as animation.

inputs.name: Directed From Center
inputs.tooltip: Make particle move away from the spawn center.

inputs.name: Turn Both Directions
inputs.tooltip: Apply randomized 1, -1 multiplier to the turning speed.

inputs.name: Bounce Friction
inputs.tooltip: Apply horizontal friction once particle stop bouncing.

inputs.name: Base Speed Over Time
inputs.tooltip: Speed may conflict with physics-based properties.

inputs.name: Step interval
inputs.tooltip:
How often the 'on step' event is triggered.
With 1 being trigger every frame, 2 means triggered once every 2 frames.

Node_Voronoi_Extra.name: Extra Voronoi
Node_Voronoi_Extra.tooltip: Random voronoi noise made with different algorithms.

Node_Warp.tooltip: Warp image by freely moving the corners.

Node_Websocket_Sender.tooltip: Create websocket server to send data to the network.

Node_Wiggler.tooltip: Create random value smoothly changing over time.

Node_Wrap_Area.name: Area Warp
